        "title": "Reading a double from a text file in java",
        "body": "<p>Can someone please explain to me why I get the error 'InputMismatchException' on the the line where I try to read in a double? Thanks!<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>        int num=inFile.nextInt();\n        for(int i=0;i&lt;num;i++){\n            String inName=inFile.next();\n            double inPrice=inFile.nextDouble();           // &lt;&lt;&lt;this line\n            Book bookInFile = new Book(inName, inPrice);\n            books.add(bookInFile);\n        }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Data in the text file:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>4\nWar and Peace\n12.99\nGreen Eggs and Ham\n3.99\nHarry Potter\n5.99\njames\n5.0\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
